<p><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">I</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:39%; padding:0in 7px 0in 7px; background-color:#d9d9d9; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top">
<p><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Mild confusion, changes in behavior, increased sleep</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:19%; padding:0in 7px 0in 7px; background-color:#d9d9d9; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top">
<p><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">No Asterixis</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
</td>
<td style="border-bottom:1px solid black; width:28%; padding:0in 7px 0in 7px; background-color:#d9d9d9; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none" valign="top">
<p><span style="page:WordSection1"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">No cerebral edema</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
</td>
